    {
      "jp": "二人は学校の外に出ました。空はまだ明るくて、道もしずかでした。二人は話しながら帰りました。けんは「また来年も体の日に来たいな」と言いました。りきぞうも「うん、いい日だったね」と言いました。夏休みは短いですが、こんな日があって、ほんとうにいい夏休みでした。",
      "en": "The two of them went out of the school. The sky was still bright, and the road was quiet. The two of them walked home together, talking as they went. Ken said, \"Next year too, I want to come to the health day.\" Rikizo also said, \"Yeah, it was a good day, wasn't it.\" Summer vacation is short, but with a day like this, it was truly a good summer vacation.",
